channel.title: Artisticy - [667/711] - Looking For Development Team!
channel.description:
[b][center][img]http://artisticy.com/forums/public/style_images/3_logo.png[/img]
Hello, I started a server called Artisticy. Im looking for some Server & Client Developers, Also Graphic artist can be accepted. The server, website & forums are currently under construction [BETA], but you can already play on our client or webclient! Currently working on Forums, Home page, Server & MAC Client. We are already hosting on a stable VPS! [b]WE HAVE A 100% FIXED TRADE (WE ARE ONE OF THE FEW 667+ HAVING THIS!)[/b]
If u would like to apply please fill in this form: AGE: ( your age ) TIME ONLINE PER DAY: ( the time u can be online on the server or u can develop ) SCRIPT LANGUAGES: ( what script languages u use, e.g. Java, php, html, Also photoshop please or cinema 4D! ) WHAT CAN U DO FOR US: ( what can you do for us? ) MSN/SKYPE: ( put your msn or skype in here! )
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/EnLlr.png[/img] --------------------------------------------------- [b][size=16pt]Welcome to Artisticy! 667 loading 711![/size][/b] ---------------------------------------------------
[b]Homepage: [url=http://www.artisticy.com]Click Here[/url] Forums: [url=http://www.artisticy.com/forums/]Click Here[/url] Webclient: [url=http://www.artisticy.com/webclient/play.php]Click Here[/url] Download Client: [url=http://www.artisticy.com/downloads/Artisticy_client.jar]Click Here[/url][/b]
--------------------------------------------------- [b]Server Features/Includes:[/b] [b]100% Working Trade Fixed drop picking up Duel Arena Working bank booths! 24/7 Hosted on a VPS Awesome Home Almost all skills working! Good Economy Perfect EXP Rates Full Godwars 100% Working Nex Many mini-games Awesome training area (::train) Webclient (working with both java 6 & 7) Friendly staff No lag Perfect switching All the newest runescape armours[/b] [b]And much more![/b] ---------------------------------------------------
